  - component: {fileID: 1939806494}
  - component: {fileID: 1939806493}
  - component: {fileID: 1939806492}
  - component: {fileID: 1939806491}
  - component: {fileID: 1939806490}
  m_Layer: 0
  m_Name: Harlow (1)
  m_TagString: NPC
  m_Icon: {fileID: 0}
  m_NavMeshLayer: 0
  m_StaticEditorFlags: 0
  m_IsActive: 1
--- !u!114 &1939806490
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1939806489}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: b3084848c5897dd41b9239769188f1bd, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  npcName: DR. HARLOW
  conversation:
  - characterName: DETECTIVE
    sentence: Hey. You doing okay?
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: DR. HARLOW
    sentence: Ah, Hello. I'm the Institute's curator. Was the Institute's curator,
      apparently.
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: DETECTIVE
    sentence: That announcement caught you off guard?
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: 'DR. HARLOW '
    sentence: Completely. Nineteen years overseeing this collection, and I find out
      its fate alongside the others. Efficient, if nothing else. And you are?
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: DETECTIVE
    sentence: Just another guest.
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: DETECTIVE
    sentence: "I thought as much. Max has a habit of surrounding himself with people
      who make him look credible. Scholars, artists\u2026 specialists."
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: DETECTIVE
    sentence: Is that what I am? Set dressing?
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: DR. HARLOW
    sentence: "I\u2019ve been dressing for nineteen years. Don\u2019t take it personally. "
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: DR. HARLOW
    sentence: "Max collects people the same way he collects artifacts. He finds something
      impressive, acquires it, and puts it on display. And when he\u2019s finished
      with it, he discards it on a Friday."
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: DETECTIVE
    sentence: You really had no idea about the university?
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: DR. HARLOW
    sentence: "Found out the same time you did. Every piece in this building passed
      through my hands\u2026 I\u2019ll be sorry to see it go."
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: DETECTIVE
    sentence: What do you think he actually wants with the university?
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: DR. HARLOW
    sentence: His name on a building. That's all it's ever been. The collection was
      never about history for Max. It was about ownership.
    isItalic: 0
  - characterName: DR. HARLOW
    sentence: Anyway, lovely to meet you. I just wish it were under better circumstances.
    isItalic: 0
